'a'yUrKH LPhNYV MShPhT VPhY 'aML'a ThVKChVTh.
'aD'yH MLYM Y'yNNY V'aBYNH MH-Y'aMUr LY.
HBUrB-KCh YUrYB 'yMDY L'a 'aK-HV'a YShM BY.
ShM YShUr NVKCh 'yMV V'aPhLTH LNTShCh MShPhTY.
HN QDM 'aHLK V'aYNNV V'aChVUr VL'a-'aBYN LV.
ShM'aVL B'yShThV VL'a-'aChZ Y'yTPh YMYN VL'a 'aUr'aH.
KY-YD'y DUrK 'yMDY BChNNY KZHB 'aTSh'a.
B'aShUrV 'aChZH UrGLY DUrKV ShMUrThY VL'a-'aT.
